functional Oriented Programming:
-----------------------------------
1. write a global funtion
2. call the global function



function:
------------
is a block of code shared under a name.

adv:
----
write code one time and reuse for any number of times

"""
syntax:

def <function_name>(<arguments>) :
    <function body>
"""
1. def keyword to write a function
2. after def specify funtion name
3. function can take any data type and can return any data type
use the indentation for the function body
